[DhtmlXQ_comment0]sg 20120310 2010 cnscr4 ||Zheng Weitong W Lv Qin||Round 4 of the 2010 Chinese National Singles Xiangqi Championships and one of the hottest rising stars faces one of the best in the history of the sport: Sichuan Province's Master Zheng Weitong takes red to go against GM Lv Qin.||Prior to the National Singles Competition, Master Zheng Weitong just won the 2010 Yang Guanlin Cup, another prestigious event and was in superb form.||This game was commented by Master Huang Hailin and GM Zhao Xinxin.[/DhtmlXQ_comment0]
[DhtmlXQ_comment1]The Angel's Pawn or Angel's Guide according to the WXF, is a favorite opening of Zheng. And faced with one of the best in the history of the sport, Master Zheng gives his best...[/DhtmlXQ_comment1]
